r (through life)’, which was a favourite name among early Christians. This was then altered by association with Latin <i>Beatus</i> ‘blessed’ (<i>Via-</i> and <i>Bea-</i> sometimes being pronounced the same in Late Latin).  See also  Beatrice ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Beatrix Frecie was born about 1265, in Shropshire, England, United Kingdom as the daughter of Ingram de Frecie. She married William Coningsby on 25 January 1299. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"Abt 1265–":"umbes 1265–Surnud","1265–Female":"1265–Surnud","1265–1351":"1265–1351","1310–Male":"1310–Surnud","1240–Male":"1240–Surnud","Abt 1310":"umbes 1310","Abt 1265":"umbes 1265","1310":"1310","1265":"1265","25 Jan 1299":"25. jaanuar 1299","1351":"1351","1240":"1240","Nene Solers, Shropshire, England":"Shropshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1265–":"noin 1265–Kuollut","1265–Female":"1265–Kuollut","1265–1351":"1265–1351","1310–Male":"1310–Kuollut","1240–Male":"1240–Kuollut","Abt 1310":"noin 1310","Abt 1265":"noin 1265","1310":"1310","1265":"1265","25 Jan 1299":"25. tammikuuta 1299","1351":"1351","1240":"1240","Nene Solers, Shropshire, England":"Shropshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1265–":"environ 1265–Décédée","1265–Female":"1265–Décédée","1265–1351":"1265–1351","1310–Male":"1310–Décédé","1240–Male":"1240–Décédé","Abt 1310":"environ 1310","Abt 1265":"environ 1265","1310":"1310","1265":"1265","25 Jan 1299":"25 janvier 1299","1351":"1351","1240":"1240","Nene Solers, Shropshire, England":"Shropshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Beatrix Frecie est née environ 1265, à Shropshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, fille de Ingram de Frecie. Elle a épousé William Coningsby le 25 janvier 1299. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"Abt 1265–":"um 1265–Verstorben","1265–Female":"1265–Verstorben","1265–1351":"1265–1351","1310–Male":"1310–Verstorben","1240–Male":"1240–Verstorben","Abt 1310":"um 1310","Abt 1265":"um 1265","1310":"1310","1265":"1265","25 Jan 12